; Coverage test for account.cc lines 385-395:
; Exercise fn_all() for accounts via account check directive.
; Using check (not assert) to avoid error exit; check just warns.

account Assets:Cash
    check all(amount < $0)

2024/01/01 Test One
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/15 Test Two
    Expenses:Food    $20.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Assets
24-Jan-01 Test One              Assets:Cash                 $-10.00      $-10.00
24-Jan-15 Test Two              Assets:Cash                 $-20.00      $-30.00
__ERROR__
Warning: "$FILE", line 8: Transaction check failed: all((amount < {$0.00}))
  (check expression at "$FILE", line 5)
Warning: "$FILE", line 12: Transaction check failed: all((amount < {$0.00}))
  (check expression at "$FILE", line 5)
end test
